OL,3,CWho are the Alba Party and how have
OL,4,Cthey become Scotland's kingmaker?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FScotland's Alba Party only formed in
OL,10,F2021, but it is poised to play
OL,11,Fkingmaker as current First Minister
OL,12,FHumza Yousaf.
OL,14,FMr Yousaf is facing a at Holyrood
OL,15,Ffollowing the collapse of the power-
OL,16,Fsharing deal between the SNP and
OL,17,FScottish Greens.
