OL,3,CWho are the Alba Party and how have
OL,4,Cthey become Scotland's kingmaker?
OL,6,FAlba Party Holyrood leader Ash Regan
OL,7,Fis yet to say how she would vote, but
OL,8,Fit's thought she will be hugely
OL,9,Finfluential in terms of whether he
OL,10,Fremains in charge.
OL,12,FSo where did the party come from, who
OL,13,Fare its members and what role could it
OL,14,Fplay in Scotland's political future?
OL,16,FWhere did the Alba Party come from?
OL,18,FThe Alba Party was founded in 2021 by
OL,19,FLaurie Flynn, a former TV producer,
OL,20,Fwith former First Minister Alex
OL,21,FSalmond appointed as party leader.
