OL,3,CWho are the Alba Party and how have
OL,4,Cthey become Scotland's kingmaker?
OL,6,FMr Salmond had been leader of the
OL,7,FScottish National Party before Nicola
OL,8,FSturgeon and led the party and country
OL,9,Fas first minister from 2007 to 2014.
OL,11,FThe following description of the
OL,12,Fparty's goals was laid out when it was
OL,13,Ffounded: "The sole purpose of Alba is
OL,14,Fto strengthen and deepen the movement
OL,15,Ffor independence through an unstinting
OL,16,Fgenerosity of spirit, active and
OL,17,Flawful campaigning and the extension
OL,18,Fof our just and democratic
OL,19,Finstitutions so that they are fit for
OL,20,Fthe 21st century and beyond."
