OL,3,CWho are the Alba Party and how have
OL,4,Cthey become Scotland's kingmaker?
OL,6,FA number of politicians have defected
OL,7,Fto Alba from other parties since it
OL,8,Fwas established, including MPs Neale
OL,9,FHanvey and Kenny MacAskill who were
OL,10,Fboth initially elected as members of
OL,11,Fthe SNP.
OL,13,FThe most prominent defection was Ash
OL,14,FRegan, who left the SNP after failing
OL,15,Fto win the party's leadership election
OL,16,Fand became its Holyrood leader as the
OL,17,Fonly MSP.
OL,19,FMr Yousaf described Ms Regan's
OL,20,Fdeparture from the SNP as "no great
OL,21,Floss" to the party.
