OL,3,CWho are the Alba Party and how have
OL,4,Cthey become Scotland's kingmaker?
OL,6,FHow powerful is the Alba Party?
OL,8,FThe Alba Party only has one MSP out of
OL,9,Fits 129 seats, but despite its small
OL,10,Fsize, it does have the power to shape
OL,11,FScotland's current political landscape.
OL,13,FFor example in the context of a no-
OL,14,Fconfidence vote in Mr Humza Yousaf, he
OL,15,Fwould need at least 64 of the 129 MSPs
OL,16,Fto vote for him in order to gain a
OL,17,Fmajority to win the vote.
