OL,3,CWho are the Alba Party and how have
OL,4,Cthey become Scotland's kingmaker?
OL,6,FThe SNP has 63 MSPs, leaving Mr Yousaf
OL,7,Fone short of the minimum tally he
OL,8,Fneeds to reach, meaning the one vote
OL,9,Ffrom Ash Regan could make the
OL,10,Fdifference between a victory and a
OL,11,Floss for the current first minister.
OL,13,FThe Scottish Greens, who had been in a
OL,14,Fcoalition government with the SNP,
OL,15,Fsided with the Conservatives, Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrats and Labour parties .
OL,18,FAlba leader Mr Salmond said Ms Regan
OL,19,Fis now the "most powerful MSP in the
OL,20,FScottish Parliament".
