OL,3,CWho are the Alba Party and how have
OL,4,Cthey become Scotland's kingmaker?
OL,6,FAnother prominent figure who has
OL,7,Fweighed in on the debate is author JK
OL,8,FRowling, who wrote a post on X
OL,9,Fsuggesting that "the idea that Humza
OL,10,FYousaf's political fate may now lie in
OL,11,Fthe hands of Ash Regan" is "karma".
OL,13,FShe has been very vocal about the
OL,14,FSNP's stance on gender and their plans
OL,15,Fto implement gender self-
OL,16,Fidentification.
OL,18,FWill the Alba Party be the downfall of
OL,19,FHumza Yousaf?
