OL,3,CWho are the Alba Party and how have
OL,4,Cthey become Scotland's kingmaker?
OL,6,FWhile there has been no confirmation
OL,7,Fas to how Ms Regan will cast her
OL,8,Fballot in a no-confidence vote, she
OL,9,Fhas sent a letter to the first
OL,10,Fminister requesting "a reset".
OL,12,F"Scotland deserves and demands a
OL,13,Freset," Ms Regan wrote in her letter.
OL,14,F"I am open to talking to anyone across
OL,15,Fthis chamber who will prioritise
OL,16,Fprogress on what we were elected to
OL,17,Fdeliver for our constituents and
OL,18,FScotland."
