OL,3,CWho are the Alba Party and how have
OL,4,Cthey become Scotland's kingmaker?
OL,6,FShe offered Mr Yousaf an "early
OL,7,Fopportunity" to discuss three clear
OL,8,Fpriorities ` Scottish independence,
OL,9,Fwomen's rights and the future of the
OL,10,FGrangemouth oil refinery.
OL,12,FIn a letter to Alba members, Ms Regan
OL,13,Fsaid she is "carefully considering"
OL,14,Fher position ahead of the vote.
OL,16,FHumza Yousaf meanwhile has said he
OL,17,Fintends to carry on as first minister
OL,18,Fand fight for his leadership, and
OL,19,Fhopes that he will be able to persuade
OL,20,Fthe Scottish Greens to back away from
OL,21,Fa no-confidence vote.
